title: You Say Party We Say Die - Remik's Cube
description:
Remik's Cube is the third album by You Say Party! We Say Die!, released digital-only on Paper Bag Digital on August 26, 2008. Remik's Cube is a reworking of their previous album Lose All Time. [1]
